| ---------------------- | -------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| `domain-models.md`     | None           | ŌĆö                                               |
| `domain-policies.md`   | ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ only        | Blockquote callouts for critical caveats only   |
| `database-tables.md`   | None           | ŌĆö                                               |
| `retry-policies.md`    | None           | ŌĆö                                               |
| `http-contracts.md`    | None           | ŌĆö                                               |
| `event-consumers.md`   | None           | ŌĆö                                               |

**For new spec types:** default is no emojis. If a use case requires ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ callouts, declare it in the spec type's `## Anti patterns` section and add a row here. No emoji other than ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ is ever permitted in any spec file.

The first bullet of every `**Avoid these...**` anti-pattern section must always state the emoji rule explicitly.

