## Language rules

| Rule                        | Correct                                              | Incorrect                                  |
| --------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| Tense in descriptions       | Present tense: "Stores participant sessions"         | "Will store", "Was used to"                |
| Voice in best practices     | Imperative: "Document every field"                  | "You should document", "Fields are documented" |
| Length of descriptions      | One or two sentences maximum                        | Multi-sentence paragraphs                  |
| Business vs technical focus | "Participant is banned from the room"               | "Status enum is set to BANNED in DynamoDB" |
| Required column values      | `Yes` or `No` ŌĆö never "Required", "Optional"        | "Mandatory", "Optional", blank             |
| Spec file titles            | No `#` H1 heading ŌĆö files start at `## overview`    | `# ParticipantSchema`                      |

